624
00:35:10,660 --> 00:35:12,300
That's why in those

625
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:13,660
martial arts novels,

626
00:35:13,860 --> 00:35:15,260
the prettier the woman,

627
00:35:15,260 --> 00:35:16,740
