628
00:35:17,100 --> 00:35:17,940
See?

629
00:35:18,540 --> 00:35:19,820
You young people,

630
00:35:20,140 --> 00:35:21,420
before you get married,

631
00:35:21,420 --> 00:35:22,660
you must go to the hospital

632
00:35:22,660 --> 00:35:24,300
