633
00:35:24,500 --> 00:35:26,200
You must check thoroughly
before you get married.

634
00:35:30,180 --> 00:35:31,980
How do men get checked?

635
00:35:37,100 --> 00:35:38,500
For men,

636
00:35:39,060 --> 00:35:40,500
