00:37:01,580 --> 00:37:02,740
Why the hospital?

647
00:37:02,980 --> 00:37:03,980
To see a psychiatrist.

648
00:37:04,220 --> 00:37:05,060
Come on,

649
00:37:05,380 --> 00:37:07,140
Bai Lan, I'm serious.

650
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:09,660
